Package: r4subui
Title: Interactive Dashboard for Clinical Submission Readiness
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R:
    person("Pawan Rama", "Mali", email = "prm@outlook.in",
           role = c("aut", "cre", "cph"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0001-7864-5819"))
Description: Provides an interactive Shiny dashboard for the R4SUB (R for
    Regulatory Submission) ecosystem. Visualizes evidence tables, pillar
    scores, the Submission Confidence Index (SCI), risk registers,
    traceability coverage, and trend analysis. Supports upload of evidence data
    or direct integration with 'r4subcore', 'r4subtrace', 'r4subrisk', and
    'r4subscore'.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
URL: https://r4sub.github.io/r4subui/, https://github.com/R4SUB/r4subui
